highlights.text: “Âm Thầm Bên Em” by Sơn Tùng M-TP has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 1718 days straight.
EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “NGƯỜI ĐẦU TIÊN” is the highest at #3.
“Thịnh Vượng Việt Nam Sáng Ngời” by buitruonglinh is the highest new entry on Top Songs Vietnam at #176.
“ex's hate me, Pt.2” by AMEE is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 80 spots at #96.
